---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="页面未找到" description="抱歉，页面不存在。">
  <div class="py-16 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-muted">404</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">页面未找到</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">链接可能已失效，试试返回首页或使用搜索。</p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary">
      <a class="underline" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="underline" href="/search/">站内搜索</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
